    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832270/extras/be9bcd98034e7dd7a205e82d82647c16.avif?t=1729796238\" width=464 height=95 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In a distant kingdom, a young monk dedicates himself to training to become a powerful wizard. However, evil monsters begin to haunt his peaceful land. Now, he must embark on a journey and face unimaginable dangers to uncover the origin of the evil.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHOOT LIGHT AGAINST STRUCTURES AND MONSTERS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can deal damage to monsters or interact with structures by shooting at them with your light shot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832270/extras/076a81648fa52ee27eb1838b54d660cd.avif?t=1729796238\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MOVE QUICKLY BETWEEN WHITE FLAMES USING TELEPORT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By pressing the right mouse button you will be instantly transported to the white flame.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832270/extras/d4310ba803d6bc9f70ac96744c9489a5.avif?t=1729796238\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >INTERACT WITH SPELLS OF DIFFERENT COLORS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blue spells were cast by allies while the reds were cast by enemies. Discover the function of each spell during the journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1832270/extras/566a7e33f601b29fb87599f89177e1c7.avif?t=1729796238\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
